<author>rḍạ rmsys, rḍạ rmsys</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ yswʿ hnạk fy ạlṣlyb .. rfʿt ʿny yạ ḥbyb
 yạ ḥbyby tḥmlt ạlậlậm .. ltmnḥny ạlslạm
 ạlqrạr- fsẖkẖṣk yḥlw lfw̉ạdy
 wḥbk ymlạ̉ kyạny
 ạ̉lmsh ạ̉ḥsh yḥyṭ bḥyạty
 fhw gẖdẖạỷy yjry fy dmạỷy
 bgẖyrh lạ ạstṭyʿ ạlḥyạẗ
 2- fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ ạlrhyb .. mḍyt tdfʿ ạlqṣạṣ
 ʿndmạ qd smrwạ ydyk .. ạ̉ṭʿt ftm ạlkẖlạṣ
 3- fy ạlṣlyb rạ̉ytk hnạk .. tḥbny mn qlbk
 yạ ḥbyby lm tnsny hnạk .. bạlrgẖm mn ậlạmk
 4- nhr ḥbiⁿ jạrfiⁿ qwy .. jry̱ mn jnbk ạlṭʿyn
 fdmạk tḥml ạlkẖlạṣ .. lkl kẖạṭyiⁿ̉ ạ̉tẖym</lyrics>
<title>yạ yswʿ hnạk fy ạlṣlyb</title>
</song>